metadata.name: 48 chances not to die
metadata.description:
"48 chances not to die"
This art was created from 48 video segments for over 4 years, where a popular guy Nikita Deft is one step away from death performing various movements(Backflip, walking on hands, acrobatic stunts, riding a scooter) on the edge of various skyscrapers in the world(Dubai, Shangai, Bangkok, Moscow).
 Many of these moments were featured on the covers of the world's publications such as the Daily Mail and others:

https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5794633/Daredevil-rides-edge-40-storey-high-building-scooter-wobbling-beams.html

https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6287541/Daredevil-scales-77-storey-skyscraper-Dubai-without-safety-gear.html

https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/daredevil-scales-giant-sk

...

This is the basis and license from incredible film called "I'm so high - Nikita Deft". 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ChEi2iym4qg

You can check the original of each video fragment there. After this NFT, you also get the rights to own this movie.
